name: Survival War Plane - Fly Through Obstacles
name_original: Survival War Plane - Fly Through Obstacles
description:
We have to warn you - this game is extremely addictive!

Want to know how good are you at flying planes? Survival War Plane - Fly Through Obstacles will test them!

Fun and addictive game!

How to play: how with your finger and lead the plane in any direction.

It might look easy but it is not.

Try it and you will love it instantly!

Train your logic, math, visual and focus skills!

Survival War Plane - Fly Through Obstacles is waiting for you.

If you love it - leave a rating!
